1
00:00:00,200 --> 00:00:01,840
Aku terjatuhkan kunci kereta dalam kolam ni.

2
00:00:02,160 --> 00:00:04,040
Rasanya awak kena bertanggungjawab.

3
00:00:04,160 --> 00:00:05,440
Ini nombor peribadi saya.

4
00:00:05,640 --> 00:00:06,600
Boleh kalau saya hubungi awak untuk bercinta?

5
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:07,680
Silakan.

6
00:00:10,040 --> 00:00:11,000
Awak nak kahwin dengan saya?

7
00:00:11,160 --> 00:00:11,760
Ya, saya nak.

8
00:00:12,040 --> 00:00:12,600
Sial!

9
00:00:12,680 --> 00:00:13,240
Hei.

10
00:00:14,440 --> 00:00:15,840
Awak kena buka baju.

11
00:00:15,960 --> 00:00:17,040
Awak tak nak jatuh sakit, kan?

12
00:00:17,240 --> 00:00:20,640
Bila awak tahu
awak nak kahwin dengan Tim?

13
00:00:21,080 --> 00:00:23,640
Saya cuma tahu saya nak dengan dia setiap hari.

14
00:00:24,520 --> 00:00:25,720
Awak nak kahwin dengan saya?

15
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:27,360
JEERAMONGKOLTHANUN

16
00:00:27,520 --> 00:00:28,440
Sepuluh bilion?

17
00:00:32,560 --> 00:00:34,240
PERMAIN DENGAN PERASAAN DIA,
BUKAN PERASAAN KAU.

18
00:00:34,880 --> 00:00:36,240
JANGAN ANGGAP PAI COMEL!

19
00:00:41,560 --> 00:00:43,600
JANGAN JATUH CINTA PADA SASARAN
WALAU APA PUN!

20
00:00:48,880 --> 00:00:49,920
Kenapa nak tahan diri?

21
00:00:50,120 --> 00:00:51,280
Kita akan kahwin tak lama lagi.

22
00:00:52,560 --> 00:00:53,400
Ah, pedulikanlah.

23
00:00:57,840 --> 00:00:59,360
Jangan jatuh cinta pada sasaran.

24
00:01:13,360 --> 00:01:14,000
Helo?

25
00:01:14,320 --> 00:01:15,040
Oom?

26
00:01:16,160 --> 00:01:17,080
Esok awak lapang?

27
00:01:18,240 --> 00:01:19,240
Aku ada kerja untuk awak.

28
00:01:20,720 --> 00:01:21,360
Baik.

29
00:01:32,480 --> 00:01:37,280
Saya datang untuk meminang Pai
untuk Tim secara rasmi.

30
00:01:42,440 --> 00:01:44,160
Sangat gembira bertemu.

31
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:47,480
Kita semua dah nampak Tim sangat konsisten.

32
00:01:47,880 --> 00:01:49,560
Kami tak ada bantahan langsung.

33
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:53,080
Betul.

34
00:01:53,440 --> 00:01:54,480
Betul, sayang?

35
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:58,440
Terima kasih, Atuk, dan juga
Papa dan Mama.

36
00:01:59,360 --> 00:02:01,280
Saya sangat bersyukur dengar begitu,

37
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:04,280
lagi-lagi lepas dengar Tim
asyik puji Pai je.

38
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:08,160
Masa mereka mula bercinta,
Tim telefon saya tiap hari

39
00:02:08,320 --> 00:02:11,480
tanya macam mana ayah dia dulu
pikat saya masa bercinta.

40
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:12,880
Dia ingat nak guna helah yang sama, agaknya.

41
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:16,800
Betul ke?

42
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:19,840
Mungkin sikit.

43
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,160
Biar saya ambilkan untuk awak.

44
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:25,520
Ini, Mak.

45
00:02:26,160 --> 00:02:26,840
Terima kasih, sayang.

46
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:28,360
Tapi awak tak perlu risau pasal saya.

47
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:29,800
Awak jaga Pai elok-elok.

48
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:32,080
Maaf. Boleh minta garpu?

49
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:36,480
Makcik, Da Zhan dah besar.

50
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:39,280
Biar dia cuba guna chopstick,
baru dia pandai guna.

51
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:43,120
Oh, jangan marah sepupu awak
kalau teman lelaki awak buatkan untuk awak.

52
00:02:44,720 --> 00:02:45,880
Saya ambilkan makanan untuk dia.

53
00:02:46,880 --> 00:02:47,960
Da Zhan nak apa?

54
00:02:48,440 --> 00:02:49,080
Har gow, ya.

55
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:49,480
Okey.

56
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:51,240
Err...

57
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:54,760
Nah.

58
00:02:55,040 --> 00:02:55,880
Terima kasih.

59
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:58,560
Nanti saya ajar awak
guna chopstick, boleh?

60
00:02:59,040 --> 00:02:59,600
Tak nak.

61
00:03:00,320 --> 00:03:00,800
Tak?

62
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:09,920
Nah.

63
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:13,360
Awak bagi saya dua-dua bahagian leher ikan?

64
00:03:14,040 --> 00:03:15,280
Biar saya kongsi satu dengan awak.

65
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:16,200
Terima kasih.

66
00:03:23,040 --> 00:03:25,040
Lain kali saya bagi dua lagi.

67
00:04:48,520 --> 00:04:50,800
Maaf sangat saya tak dapat ikut awak hari ni.

68
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,640
Oh, tak apa, sayang.

69
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:54,040
Awak patut luang masa dengan keluarga awak.

70
00:04:54,320 --> 00:04:56,400
Hari ni pun saya dah sangat gembira.

71
00:04:56,520 --> 00:04:57,760
Saya teramat gembira.

72
00:04:58,360 --> 00:05:00,320
Saya akan senyum sampai balik ke London.

73
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:05,240
Kalau Tim menyusahkan,
awak kena beritahu saya, sayang.

74
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:06,280
Mestilah.

75
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:08,040
Nanti awak kena.

76
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:10,440
Mak.

77
00:05:10,760 --> 00:05:12,720
Tak rasa cepat sangat sayang Pai
lebih daripada anak sendiri?

78
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,680
Apa yang tak boleh disayangi pasal dia, betul tak?

79
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:18,680
Selamat jalan, Mak.

80
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:19,040
Mestilah.

81
00:05:19,440 --> 00:05:20,360
Saya kena pergi dulu.

82
00:05:21,400 --> 00:05:22,400
Jumpa nanti.

83
00:05:31,440 --> 00:05:32,320
Awak pasti awak okey?

84
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:33,720
Emm.

85
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:35,520
Semua orang nampak
mood baik hari ni.

86
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:37,440
Saya rasa takkan ada apa-apa
yang buat pening kepala.

87
00:05:38,280 --> 00:05:40,320
Telefon saya kalau ada apa-apa.

88
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:43,040
Jangan pendam sorang-sorang, faham?

89
00:05:44,400 --> 00:05:45,120
Pergilah.

90
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,040
Mak awak tunggu.

91
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:49,320
Kalau macam tu, bye.

92
00:05:51,280 --> 00:05:51,920
Tim!

93
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:20,320
Ruginya.

94
00:06:20,640 --> 00:06:21,960
Kalau hari ni saya tak berlakon jadi orang kaya,

95
00:06:21,960 --> 00:06:25,320
saya dah suruh mereka bungkuskan
sup cendawan tu untuk saya.

96
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,160
Bagus kerja hari ni, Mama.

97
00:06:27,640 --> 00:06:29,160
Dan semua tu tanpa latihan.

98
00:06:29,520 --> 00:06:30,560
Patutlah,
nombor satu dalam industri.

99
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:32,680
Mestilah.

100
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:36,440
Dalam kerja macam ni,
kena sedia pegang apa-apa watak.

101
00:06:36,640 --> 00:06:38,400
Awak ingat kan
apa yang awak cakap pada mereka?

102
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:40,560
Awak akan jumpa mereka lagi
masa majlis kahwin nanti.

103
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:44,720
Oh, orang kaya mana kisah
setiap benda kecil sangat.

104
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:46,560
Mak Cik Kia ingat semua benda.

105
00:06:50,160 --> 00:06:52,640
Tapi budak Pai tu memang comel.

106
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:57,640
Dan saya perasan Encik Soepohn
senyum sampai ke mata bila cakap dengan awak.

107
00:06:57,760 --> 00:06:59,200
Nampak macam dia betul-betul sayang awak.

108
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:01,400
Mestilah.

109
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:03,560
Itulah tujuan penipuan ni.

110
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:06,760
Tapi sejujurnya.

111
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:11,360
Kenapa tak bercinta betul-betul
dan hidup dengan dia?

112
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:13,680
Gila kalau saya buat macam tu.

113
00:07:14,400 --> 00:07:15,960
Kalau semua ni terbongkar,

114
00:07:15,960 --> 00:07:17,920
orang macam mereka
boleh hancurkan hidup saya.

115
00:07:18,840 --> 00:07:20,720
Sayang, kan.

116
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:22,880
Kamu berdua ada serasi.

117
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:25,720
Ini gaji awak.

118
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:29,800
Terbaik.

119
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:30,520
Terima kasih.

120
00:07:30,880 --> 00:07:31,640
- Bye.
- Aku gerak dulu.

121
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:47,200
Macam mana North?

122
00:07:48,400 --> 00:07:50,200
Dia dah mula kerja di pejabat?

123
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:53,520
Saya masih cuba pujuk dia.

124
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,840
Atuk tahu dia degil macam mana.

125
00:07:55,960 --> 00:07:56,560
Pai.

126
00:07:57,440 --> 00:07:58,920
North tu budak kesian.

127
00:08:00,080 --> 00:08:04,480
Atuk takkan mati tenang
kalau tak nampak dia betulkan hidup.

128
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:07,320
Dia orang kita, Pai.

129
00:08:08,400 --> 00:08:09,600
Kita tak boleh tinggalkan dia macam tu saja.

130
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:14,400
Mestilah, Atuk.

131
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:15,960
Selamat malam.

132
00:08:33,040 --> 00:08:33,840
(Hai, sayang.)

133
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:36,160
Awak dah keluar dari lapangan terbang?

134
00:08:36,880 --> 00:08:38,280
(Sebenarnya saya masih di lapangan terbang.)

135
00:08:38,800 --> 00:08:40,280
(Awak nak saya jemput?)

136
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:41,040
(Saya boleh gerak sekarang.)

137
00:08:42,760 --> 00:08:43,480
Tak apa.

138
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:45,840
Awak patut luang masa dengan mak awak.

139
00:08:46,520 --> 00:08:47,800
Saya akan suruh pemandu hantar saya balik.

140
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:48,760
Baik.

141
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:50,560
Jumpa awak bila saya dah selesai di sini.

142
00:08:51,520 --> 00:08:52,240
Bye.

143
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:05,080
Kau menipu selamba lagi
daripada peguam macam aku, bro.

144
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:07,080
Maksud aku, aku boleh jadi peguam hebat.

145
00:09:07,400 --> 00:09:09,680
Aku boleh bela penjenayah
dan rampas kerja kau.

146
00:09:09,680 --> 00:09:10,360
Tak.

147
00:09:10,680 --> 00:09:11,480
Aku takkan benarkan.

148
00:09:11,880 --> 00:09:13,520
Kalau kau rampas kerja aku,
macam mana aku nak makan?

149
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:15,200
Dengan ais kisar, nampaknya.

150
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:17,360
Dan sedap juga.

151
00:09:20,520 --> 00:09:23,360
Tapi kenapa tak cepat balik
dan sambung perang dingin dengan Pai?

152
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:25,240
Dengar, bro.

153
00:09:25,640 --> 00:09:27,960
Aku tahu bila Pai perlukan aku,

154
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:30,120
tapi aku takkan bagi dia dapatkan
apa dia nak setiap kali.

155
00:09:30,520 --> 00:09:33,400
Ini buat dia makin nak aku,

156
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:34,600
dan tak ambil aku mudah.

157
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:37,440
Bunyi macam bagus.

158
00:09:37,760 --> 00:09:40,280
Tapi itu taktik tak guna untuk peguam.

159
00:09:41,520 --> 00:09:42,960
Guna otak sikit.

160
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:43,600
Hei.

161
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:48,120
Dah lewat.

162
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:49,400
Esok aku kena jumpa Airy.

163
00:09:50,400 --> 00:09:51,040
Baik.

164
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:56,280
Tapi ingat Peguam Prem ni
bila helah kau berantakan nanti.

165
00:09:56,680 --> 00:09:57,440
Jangan sumpah aku macam tu.

166
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:59,200
Kau nak aku tuang ais kisar
atas seluar kau, bro?

167
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:00,280
Jangan bazirkan makanan macam tu!

168
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:01,160
Aku gerak dulu.

169
00:10:01,160 --> 00:10:02,200
- Jumpa lagi.
- Semoga berjaya.

170
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:13,760
Helo, tuan.

171
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:15,560
Meja yang sama?

172
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:16,400
Ya.

173
00:10:16,680 --> 00:10:17,440
Selamat datang.

174
00:10:25,680 --> 00:10:26,680
Hong.

175
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:28,440
Airy, hai.

176
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:29,360
Duduklah.

177
00:10:32,160 --> 00:10:32,880
Hai.

178
00:10:32,880 --> 00:10:34,720
Oh, Hong.

179
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:35,160
Ya?

180
00:10:35,160 --> 00:10:36,360
Awak duduk jauh sangat dari saya.

181
00:10:36,560 --> 00:10:37,880
Macam awak langsung tak rindu saya.

182
00:10:38,400 --> 00:10:41,720
Saya cuma nak pastikan awak selesa
duduk di situ, tentu saja.

183
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:47,960
Nak cuba benda baru, atau
saya pesan hidangan kegemaran awak?

184
00:10:49,800 --> 00:10:51,800
Saya nak cuba sesuatu yang baru...

185
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:52,640
Oh?

186
00:10:52,640 --> 00:10:53,640
Macam awak, Hong.

187
00:10:58,160 --> 00:10:59,040
Awak bukan saja cantik,

188
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:01,160
tapi juga kelakar.

189
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:03,040
Mestilah.

190
00:11:03,560 --> 00:11:08,000
Saya dah habis seratus ribu untuk awak,
bukan nak pegang tangan saja, ya?

191
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:12,600
Airy, tapi awak kata saya tak sama
macam teman berbayar awak yang lain?

192
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:15,480
Awak kena pikat saya dulu, ingat?

193
00:11:17,880 --> 00:11:19,360
Pandai awak ambil hati, ya?

194
00:11:19,880 --> 00:11:21,160
Saya suka.

195
00:11:23,560 --> 00:11:24,080
Baik.

196
00:11:24,480 --> 00:11:25,880
Awak nak apa?

197
00:11:34,280 --> 00:11:35,560
DALAM KERUGIAN

198
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:52,160
Sejak hari pertama, dia langsung tak untung?

199
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:53,840
Macam mana tempat tu belum tutup lagi?

200
00:11:54,560 --> 00:11:57,000
Saya diberitahu Encik North tampung
guna duit sendiri.

201
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:02,440
Kononnya “belajar bisnes sendiri.”

202
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:05,360
Kalau macam ni, 10 tahun pun
dia takkan belajar apa-apa.

203
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:12,480
Masih tak dapat dihubungi lagi.

204
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:14,560
Bawa dia ke sini sekarang, Nana.

205
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:15,560
Baik, tuan.

206
00:12:33,520 --> 00:12:35,640
Awak masih sibuk?

207
00:12:35,800 --> 00:12:36,640
Saya tunggu di luar.

208
00:12:36,640 --> 00:12:37,440
Tim, awak boleh tinggal.

209
00:12:38,640 --> 00:12:39,440
Sekejap saja.

210
00:12:41,520 --> 00:12:42,640
Mengaku saja.

211
00:12:43,160 --> 00:12:44,200
Kau tahu kau tak boleh sorok daripada aku.

212
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:48,560
A-Awak...

213
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:49,720
Awak tahu?

214
00:12:49,960 --> 00:12:51,000
Nana dah beritahu aku semuanya.

215
00:12:57,880 --> 00:13:00,080
Salah aku sebab tak beritahu kau
sebelum aku teruskan.

216
00:13:02,280 --> 00:13:02,880
Tapi...

217
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:07,680
Aku nak kau gembira untuk aku
dan hubungan baru aku.

218
00:13:08,280 --> 00:13:10,840
SIJIL PERKAHWINAN

219
00:13:12,040 --> 00:13:12,600
Apa?!

220
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:13,280
- Apa?
- Apa?

221
00:13:19,880 --> 00:13:21,600
SIJIL PERKAHWINAN

222
00:13:23,680 --> 00:13:25,720
Tapi siapa...

223
00:13:26,160 --> 00:13:29,160
Siapa lelaki Issara Preechajit ni?

224
00:14:09,040 --> 00:14:09,600
Baik.

225
00:14:09,960 --> 00:14:10,920
Apa pun yang jadi,

226
00:14:11,560 --> 00:14:12,800
sekurang-kurangnya aku ada duit tunai.

227
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:40,760
Anak aku...

228
00:14:42,600 --> 00:14:43,680
Kita akan jadi kaya raya!

229
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:54,880
NORTH

230
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:02,600
Helo, North?

231
00:15:02,680 --> 00:15:03,720
(U, hai.)

232
00:15:03,800 --> 00:15:05,840
(Awak sibuk sekarang?)

233
00:15:06,560 --> 00:15:07,760
(Ada kecemasan.)

234
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:11,040
Oh.

235
00:15:25,720 --> 00:15:26,400
Pai, tolong bertenang—

236
00:15:26,400 --> 00:15:27,080
Siapa kau?

237
00:15:27,080 --> 00:15:28,760
Kau dari mana? Umur berapa?
Kerja apa?

238
00:15:28,920 --> 00:15:31,440
Kenapa kau kahwin dengan sepupu aku
tanpa beritahu keluarganya?

239
00:15:31,480 --> 00:15:31,920
Hah?

240
00:15:34,080 --> 00:15:34,800
Bertenang.

241
00:15:34,800 --> 00:15:36,040
Macam mana aku nak bertenang?

242
00:15:36,320 --> 00:15:37,560
North, apa yang kau fikir?

243
00:15:37,680 --> 00:15:38,680
Kau mabuk ke?

244
00:15:38,680 --> 00:15:40,720
Telefon Peguam Vicha,
kita cerai sekarang!

245
00:15:40,840 --> 00:15:42,280
Cerai? Aku tak nak cerai!

